{"tid":1658970,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"20/10百萬人大遊行後 我有新活動建議","createTime":"2019-10-16T17:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T13:10:59.000Z","uid":103102,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5f221736c85029ab321106760f51481464869614","tid":1658970,"uid":103102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:00:02.000Z","msg":"大家都知道香港人最鍾意返工，無論星期六日打生打死山崩地裂十號風球星期一都堅持要返工。既然罷工同不合作運動參與度同效率唔高，不如倒返轉搞個<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">超合作運動</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;/&mdash;&mdash;//&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-1-1&ndash;11&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">21/10 行路過海返工日</span></span><br />\n<br />\n既然大家都有共識20/10係和理非遊行，我地就早d行完返屋企休息，第二朝精神奕奕咁行路過海返工！<br />\n<br />\n首先，假日晏就遊行就見得多，平日中環快閃都試過，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">晨早流流遊行返工未聽過喇掛？</span> 呢招夠曬噱頭<br />\n<br />\n第二，我地擺明車馬行完去返工，除非政府想我地被罷工啦，否則都唔可以做d咩阻止我地，因為我地係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">行路過海返工</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n第三，行路過海除左塞路影響運輸之外，仲可以半推半就一d冇心遊行但又想快d返工既人，因為到時塞住條隧道，佢地落車行過海一定快過係巴士等<br />\n<br />\n時間地點：6:30係紅&amp;西隧口巴士站集合<br />\n                   7:00出發<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論細節<br />\n<br />\nTg:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEjddNVmKyTq4NTdEQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEjddNVmKyTq4NTdEQ&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry4oeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=43e33603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEjddNVmKyTq4NTdEQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"bcafb8280b2f1eff74374e49f23339ea16412846","tid":1658970,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:00:17.000Z","msg":"【再次有圖有真相】令街坊知道1020遊行嘅最佳方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657842</a>"},{"pid":"6b337040f1a89983402e39aa7cc5cd13516609eb","tid":1658970,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:00:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警告!!!<br />\n連登已經被狗同三毛<br />\n嚴重滲透<br />\n加上仲有分化撚<br />\n熱門一片凌亂<br />\n再咁落去唔洗林奠出手<br />\n禁我地網 封鎖連登<br />\n連登就會從內部潰散<br />\n唯有預設不推文回覆<br />\n先可以光復連登</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<code>幫手推到連仔睇到</code><br />\n<code>幫手推到連仔睇到</code><br />\n<code>幫手推到連仔睇到</code><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">建議所有回覆預設係不推文回覆</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658904</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d9e571e36b7386d07ebd89c9069fa8e85e98b14a","tid":1658970,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcafb8280b2f1eff74374e49f23339ea16412846","tid":1658970,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:00:17.000Z","msg":"【再次有圖有真相】令街坊知道1020遊行嘅最佳方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657842</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:01:13.000Z","msg":"已推"},{"pid":"8deab222a20fc39b57af39fdceab950e165475ce","tid":1658970,"uid":103102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:02:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6e47f5b4055757f7a9dda988aa36825c4928f04b","tid":1658970,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:03:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10 &middot; 20 星期日<br />\n1330 民陣九龍大遊行</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀梳士巴利道花園 -&gt; 高鐵西九龍站<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n提提大家今日有咩活動 (10 &middot; 17)<br />\n<br />\n1. 學界萬人大集會 - 1200<br />\n香港知專設計學院設計大道 HKDI<br />\n<br />\n2. 和你拖2.0 面具